## 13. Hard rules carried over from the platform

These apply to every repo; re-stated here so an agent working only in this repo can't miss them:

1. Max ~300 lines per file
2. API response shape must match `conventions/api.md`
3. Never log Stripe `client_secret` or payment payloads
4. Every tenant-scoped query filters by `restaurant_id` from trusted context, not query params
5. Never commit `.env` or secret files

See `.platform/CLAUDE.md` for the full hard constraints list.

